---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { breadcrumbSchema } from "../../utils/seo";

const siteUrl = "https://healthymindspecialists.com";
const staffName = "Dr. Grissel M. Lloyd, PsyD";
const staffRole = "Licensed Clinical Psychologist";
const staffSlug = "dr-grissel-m-lloyd-psyd";
const bannerImage =
  "https://brightervisionclients.com/resize/63bd841c407b4bb641b23b5b/attachments/c4b1165c-3f2a-47d6-999a-9932498b9ee1?top=0.0000&left=0.0000&bottom=0.5655&right=1.0000";
const tagline =
  "Working together to uncover meaning, restore balance, and create lasting change.";
const profileImage =
  "https://imagedelivery.net/B5r6pMfQRTYBHyjgaDFr8w/f2f396df-4594-4d5f-4390-c7cbc0e09b00/public";

const schemas = [
  breadcrumbSchema([
    { name: "Home", url: siteUrl },
    { name: "About Us", url: `${siteUrl}/about` },
    { name: staffName, url: `${siteUrl}/staff/${staffSlug}` },
  ]),
];
---

<Layout
  title={staffName}
  description={`Meet ${staffName}, ${staffRole} at Healthy Mind Specialists in Tampa, FL. Areas of focus include anxiety, OCD, phobias, stress management, and women's mental health.`}
  schema={schemas}
>
  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section class='relative h-[420px] md:h-[500px] overflow-hidden'>
    <img
      src={bannerImage}
      alt={`Portrait of ${staffName}, ${staffRole} at Healthy Mind Specialists`}
      width='1920'
      height='600'
      class='absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover'
      loading='eager'
    />
    <div
      class='absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-blue/80 to-brand-blue/40'
    >
    </div>
    <div class='relative h-full flex items-center'>
      <div class='max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-white'>
        <h1 class='text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display italic mb-4'>
          {staffName}
        </h1>
        <p class='text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/80 max-w-2xl'>
          {staffRole}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class='py-20 md:py-28'>
    <div class='max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6'>
      <!-- Profile + Tagline -->
      <div class='mb-12 md:flex md:items-start md:gap-10'>
        <img
          src={profileImage}
          alt={`${staffName}, ${staffRole}`}
          width='280'
          height='280'
          class='w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg mb-6 md:mb-0 mx-auto md:mx-0 flex-shrink-0'
          loading='lazy'
        />
        <div>
          <p
            class='text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display italic text-brand-blue/80'
          >
            {tagline}
          </p>
          <span class='block w-16 h-[2px] bg-brand-gold mt-6'></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio Content -->
      <div class='prose prose-lg max-w-none text-brand-blue/80 space-y-6'>
        <p>
          Reaching out for support isn't always easy, especially with someone
          who begins as a stranger. However, therapy offers something rare and
          powerful, an objective space where you can be fully seen and heard,
          free from judgment or fear that your vulnerability will be used
          against you.
        </p>
        <p>Hello, I'm Dr. Grissel Lloyd, and I'm so glad you're here.</p>
        <p>
          Life brings challenges, transitions, and internal roadblocks that can
          feel overwhelming, even when we've worked hard and done our best. In
          our work together, we'll explore the thought patterns, behavioral
          habits, and subconscious narratives that may be holding you back. It
          is my job to meet you where you are and move forward together with you
          owning the power to rewrite your life's story. My approach is
          collaborative, respectful, and deeply personalized, because your
          journey is your own, and you deserve to lead it with clarity and
          intention.
        </p>
        <p>
          My areas of focus include anxiety, OCD, specific phobias, stress
          management, and women's mental health, particularly the emotional and
          psychological impact of hormonal changes, including menopause. With a
          strong foundation in relational and behavioral work, I also specialize
          in helping individuals navigate breakups, shifting dynamics, and
          patterns that disrupt connection and growth. These moments of pain or
          uncertainty can become powerful turning points, and I am here to help
          you move through them with support and purpose.
        </p>
        <p>
          With more than 20 years in behavioral health, I bring a diverse
          clinical background to my work. I have served as a board-certified
          behavior analyst, a licensed mental health counselor, and now as a
          licensed clinical psychologist. I've had the privilege of supporting
          children, adolescents, adults, and families across community settings,
          schools, the Department of Corrections, inpatient psychiatric
          facilities, clinics, and private practice. What I've learned is that
          we are all doing the best we can with the resources we have. What do
          you do when that does not seem to be enough, or things didn't work out
          as you had hoped? Sometimes, we need a new kind of help to move
          forward.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm originally from the Caribbean, though I consider myself a citizen
          of the world. I love to travel, explore different cultures, and
          experiment with new recipes. On a typical day, you'll find me with
          friends and family, practicing Spanish, or relaxing with a good sci-fi
          or fantasy show.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you're ready to take the next step, I'm here to walk with you.
          Let's begin.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class='mt-16 text-center'>
        <a
          href='/contact'
          class='inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-brand-blue text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-brand-blue-light transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl'
        >
          Schedule a Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
